                <h1>Family Lawyer in Clifton DHA Karachi</h1>
                <p class="location-hero-description">If you live in Clifton or DHA and you're facing a difficult family matter, you don't have to go through it alone. MR Law Associates is a <strong>female-led, family-law-only firm</strong> that helps women and families across these neighborhoods with <strong>divorce and talaq, khula, child custody, maintenance and alimony, and dower (haq mehr) recovery</strong>. Led by <strong>Reema Jawed, Advocate High Court</strong>, with over 14 years of experience, we listen carefully, explain your options in plain language, and protect your rights with care and discretion.</p>

                <p class="location-hero-description">Whether you need help filing for <strong>khula</strong>, securing <strong>custody and visitation</strong> for your children, recovering <strong>unpaid dower or dowry articles</strong>, or arranging a private <strong>court marriage</strong>, our office at Tahir Plaza near the City Court is easy to reach from all of Clifton and DHA. Every case is handled confidentially, with the compassion that family matters deserve.</p>

                <div class="location-hero-cta">
                    <a href="tel:03363120798" class="btn btn-primary"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align:-0.16em"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.36 1.9.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.91.34 1.85.57 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg> Call 0336 3120798</a>
                    <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-secondary">Schedule Confidential Consultation</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Why Choose Local Lawyer -->
        <section class="benefits-section">
