                <h2>Why Families in <span class="highlight">Clifton & DHA</span> Choose Us</h2>
                <p>A caring, women-led team that handles family matters and nothing else</p>
            </div>

            <div class="benefits-grid">
                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="40" height="40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" style="display:block;margin:0 auto"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg></div>
                    <h3>Female-Led and Confidential</h3>
                    <p>Advocate Reema Jawed leads every case personally, so you can talk openly about sensitive family matters with a woman who understands. Your privacy is protected at every step, from the first call to the final hearing.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="40" height="40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" style="display:block;margin:0 auto"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg></div>
                    <h3>Serving All of Clifton and DHA</h3>
                    <p>We help women and families across Clifton Blocks 1 to 9 and every DHA phase with divorce, khula, custody, maintenance and dower matters. Wherever you are in the area, caring family-law support is close by.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="40" height="40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" style="display:block;margin:0 auto"><path d="M3 21h18"/><path d="M5 21V7l7-4 7 4v14"/><path d="M9 21v-4h6v4"/><path d="M9 10h1"/><path d="M14 10h1"/><path d="M9 14h1"/><path d="M14 14h1"/></svg></div>
                    <h3>Beside the Family Court</h3>
                    <p>Our office at Tahir Plaza sits right next to the City Court, home to the Family Courts that hear Clifton and DHA cases. That means faster filings, quick follow-ups, and less waiting for you and your children.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="40" height="40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" style="display:block;margin:0 auto"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78L12 21.23l8.84-8.84a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg></div>
